            <section class="pt-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 border-b pb-2 mb-4">2. Medical Disclaimer & Waiver (The Agreement)</h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    <p><strong>2.1 General Fitness Purpose:</strong> All training sessions and advice provided by Kubiletic are for **recreational and general fitness purposes only**.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>2.2 Medical Disclaimer:</strong> The information and training provided are **not intended as a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment**. Client understands that they must **Always seek the advice of a physician** or other qualified health provider with any questions they may have regarding a medical condition. Client agrees never to disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something learned or experienced through Kubiletic.</p>
                    
                    <p class="p-3 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
                        <strong>2.3 Assumption of Risk and Waiver:</strong> Client acknowledges that participation in any fitness program involves a **risk of injury**, including physical damage or death. By participating in Kubiletic training sessions, Client explicitly **acknowledges and accepts these risks** and agrees to **waive any claim** against Kubiletic or its trainers for any injuries or damages sustained.
                    </p>

                    <p><strong>2.4 Client Responsibility:</strong> Client agrees to **inform their trainer** of any pre-existing medical conditions, injuries, or physical limitations **before starting any exercise program** and to continuously update the trainer if any changes occur during the term of this agreement.</p>

                    <p><strong>2.5 Results:</strong> Client understands and acknowledges that results from training programs may vary and are **not guaranteed**. Consistent effort, nutrition, and lifestyle choices outside of training sessions are necessary for optimal outcomes.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Financial & Scheduling Terms -->
            <section class="pt-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 border-b pb-2 mb-4">3. Financial & Scheduling Terms</h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    <p><strong>3.1 Pricing and Payment:</strong> The Client agrees to pay for all purchased training sessions and programs in accordance with the current fee schedule provided by Kubiletic. All payments are due in advance of the session or program start date. All sales are final and non-transferable.</p>

                    <p class="p-3 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg">
                        <strong>3.2 Cancellation and Rescheduling Policy:</strong> A **minimum of 24 hours' advance notice** is required to cancel or reschedule a reserved training session. Sessions cancelled or rescheduled with less than 24 hours' notice will result in the **forfeiture of the session** and the Client will be billed for the full cost of the session. Kubiletic reserves the right to cancel or reschedule sessions as needed without penalty.
                    </p>

                    <p><strong>3.3 Late Arrival Policy:</strong> Sessions will begin and end at the scheduled time. If the Client is late, the session will be shortened accordingly, and the Client will be charged for the full session time. If the Client is more than 15 minutes late, the Trainer may, at their discretion, cancel the session, resulting in forfeiture of the session fee (as per the cancellation policy).</p>

                    <p><strong>3.4 Refund Policy:</strong> Kubiletic does not offer refunds for any reason once services have commenced or training packages have been purchased. Exceptions may be considered only in cases of documented medical emergency, at the sole discretion of Kubiletic management.</p>
                </div>
