                    <p><strong>4.1 Client Confidentiality:</strong> All personal information, health data, contact details, and fitness progress records (collectively, "Client Data") shared with Kubiletic will be kept **strictly confidential** and will only be used by Kubiletic trainers for the purpose of designing and delivering the fitness program.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>4.2 Trainer/Program Confidentiality:</strong> The Client agrees not to share or reproduce any proprietary Kubiletic training plans, methods, or documents provided by the trainer outside of their own personal use.</p>
